______________________________________________________________________-----

Based on previous work on FAT Media <http://fatmedia.com>, originally
written by Jamie Wilkinson <http://jamiedubs.com>, 
Theo Watson <http://muonics.net>, and Greg Leuch <http://gleuch.com>.

A F.A.T. Lab Production <http://fffff.at>.

______________________________________________________________________-----


Installation
  1. Unzip and upload the “fat-media” directory to your server.
  2. Put audio, video, and images or folders into the /data subdirectory.
  3. Visit yourdomain.com/fat-media — the first visit will 
     generate thumbnails!

Bonus:
  4. After the first visit, download and open a folder's info.yml to edit
     titles & descriptions.
  5. Customize config.php to your liking and create/edit your theme.


